title: Outfoxed - Rupert Murdoch's War On Journalism
description:
Outfoxed examines how media empires, led by Rupert Murdoch&#039;s Fox News, have been running a "race to the bottom" in television news. This film provides an in-depth look at Fox News and the dangers of ever-enlarging corporations taking control of the public&#039;s right to know.

Obvious and frightening accounts of how Fox News is forming your opinion.
